   <h2> 石家庄理发救女父亲牵动全城爱心 募捐已达10万 <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=4737&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=1788&amp;mobile=2" rel="nofollow" class="blue" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;margin-left:10px;">只看楼主</a> </h2> 
   <div class="plc cl" id="pid5385"> 
    <span class="avatar"><img src="http://www.hebzb.cn/uc_server/avatar.php?uid=1788&amp;size=small" style="width:32px;height:32px;" /></span> 
    <div class="display pi" href="#replybtn_5385"> 
     <ul class="authi"> 
      <li class="grey"> <em> 楼主</em><b> <a href="home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=1788&amp;mobile=2" class="blue">就是001</a></b> </li> 
