     <div class="message"> 
      <strong><br /> </strong>
      <a href="http://www.hebzb.cn/&quot; target=" target="_blank"><font color="#0066cc">本地</font></a>
      <a href="http://www.chinanews.com/" target="_blank"><font color="#0066cc">中新网</font></a>李洋2015-06-07 07:55 
